    <arm_group_label>2.</arm_group_label>
  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Use of soft contact lenses (e.g. silicone hydrogel lenses, daily disposables etc.) and
             multipurpose solution for cleaning, including enzyme-based cleaners (ClearCare etc.)

          -  Able to wear contact lenses for approximately 10-12 hours/day

          -  Willingness to complete entire length of trial and comply with subjective
             questionnaire.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients taking topical cyclosporine (Restasis)

          -  Patients currently using Optive for dryness relief.

          -  Patients wearing hard or rigid gas permeable lenses

          -  Patients with uncontrolled systemic disease which may confound the results of the
             trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
